edu.nyu.cs.addressbook.search.impl

Class ContactField.ContactFieldBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.nyu.cs.addressbook.search.impl.ContactField.ContactFieldBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Builder<ContactField>
    Enclosing class:
    ContactField

    public static class ContactField.ContactFieldBuilder
extends Object
implements Builder<ContactField>
    Author:
    shenli

    The ContactFieldBuilder class represents building contact matcher criteria information.

    ContactFieldBuilder objects are not constant; their values could be changed after they are created. The ContactFieldBuilder object is not thread-safe. To use it concurrently, user must surround each method invocation with external synchronization of the users' choosing.
